{
  "stem": "21013.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't really remember that I was unhappy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was a very good student and sort of a goody-goody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was very strictly brought up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And my parents insisted that I excel in school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because I was weak in math, I had a tutor at the age of 10 in math in order to get top grades, because they insisted that I study hard.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very well at first, until the political situation became such that they took sides.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we would go to major rallies in Vienna, let's say on the 1st of May, which was the workers' Labor Day.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And instead of singing the Austrian anthem, they would [SIGHS] put the words of the German anthem in, because it was the same tune.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The music was the same of the German anthem and the Austrian, so they exchanged a word.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Instead of singing about Austria, they sang about Deutschland, Deutschland, uber alles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they took sides.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was whispering.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was discriminated against in games and in sports.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was very good at certain sports and they wouldn't pick me as a captain or whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was very apparent that there was a lot of discrimination.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think when I was about 12.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was '33, '34, when Hitler first came into Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was the underground movement.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't really expect any re-unification of the Third Reich at that time yet.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they were inclined to be very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I always wanted to be an artist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that was the only goals I had.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- I was very interested in children's groups that my parents put me into to fight against ever having another war.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we sang songs about never having war again.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
